android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.aurum.permission.C2D_MESSAGE.description: Allows the application to receive push notifications.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

com.huawei.android.launcher.permission.W.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

com.oppo.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTI.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

playstore_details.title: Aurum - best affordable therapy, stress, anxiety.
playstore_details.description:
Welcome to Aurum, the platform which provides the best professional mental and emotional wellness ecosystem. Now manage your stress, anxiety, worry through our very popular programs. Get affordable therapy and access to expert psychologists through our app. Our users love us because we make it so easy and convenient to get access to quality care and help. Go on and be the best version of yourself. Right away. All our professionals are based out of India and are qualified experts.

Programs -
These are specially designed self-educating modules based on proven techniques like Cognitive Behavior Therapy(CBT), Mindfulness, Meditation and others which will help you learn the skills to cope with your issues. Be it stress, anxiety or relationships, you can learn at your own speed and master the skills required to face these problems. The best part is you will always have your coach - who is a certified psychologist, available on chat 24 * 7. Your coach will guide you throughout and help you achieve emotional and mental stability.

Therapy -
There are various incidents or situations in life where we can't seem to find our way out. The mental and emotional pressure becomes too much to handle. If you feel like you are going through a tough period of grief, sadness, anger, stress, anxiety, depression, worry etc connect with one of our qualified therapists at a fraction of the cost of traditional therapy. Your coach will be there for you round the clock, making sure you live your life in the best way possible. Getting access to a professional psychologist has never been so simple, easy and affordable.

*Now share positive affirmations with your loved ones and develop a positive mindset and learn how to have positive thoughts with expert guidance and self-help tools.*

We have created an entire ecosystem for you to get all the things necessary to become the best version of yourself. Solutions for Depression, CBT, Positive Affirmations, Life Coaching, Positive Mindset, Loneliness, Relationships, Mindfulness, Meditation, Therapy. Download now!
